body_html: Doing a compare of the files replaced by the command provided by @fischman with the files in the Debian/Ubuntu package libgcc-5-dev 5.5.0-12ubuntu1 they appear to be compatible. The only changes I found diffing the two copies with meld were some variables renamed within the functions (adding __ in some places) and the problematic type changes. While hacky and not recommended as a blanket fix it does seem to solve the problem and shouldn't cause new issues in this particular scenario.
